name: 3D Frog Feast
description:
The frog is hungry. Really hungry. Help the frog gobble up all the food in super cool looking 3D mazes!

Watch out for snakes! While the frog is eating the food, the snakes try to eat the frog. Only when the frog eats a special power vitamin can he turn the tables on the snakes. Clear all the mazes to become top frog champion and earn your place among your peers.

This game is filled with super retro arcade action and hilarious fun!

Features:

* 31 amazing mazes
* Different worlds to explore:
- The Beach
- The Woods
- Haunted Forest
- The North Pole
- The Castle
- Under the Sea
- The Circus
- and more...
* High-scores table
* Super addicting game-play
* Retro arcade action
* Cool soundtrack
* Super cool frog
